msgid "Please enter a title."
msgstr "请输入标题。"

msgid "Write a complete, well-structured article with the title: \"%1$s\"%2$s%3$s\n\nReturn your response as a JSON object with this exact structure:\n{\n  \"title\": \"Your suggested title (can refine the original)\",\n  \"content\": \"Full article content in markdown format (do NOT include the title as H1)\",\n  \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\", \"tag3\"]\n}\n\nRequirements:\n- Use proper headings (H2 for sections, H3 for subsections)\n- Include an introduction and conclusion\n- Write in a professional yet engaging tone\n- Aim for 800-1500 words\n- Use markdown formatting\n- Suggest 3-5 relevant tags\n- Only return the JSON object, nothing else"
msgstr "撰写一篇标题为 \"%1$s\" 的完整、结构清晰的文章。%2$s%3$s\n\n请以 JSON 格式返回，结构如下：\n{\n  \"title\": \"建议的标题（可优化原标题）\",\n  \"content\": \"完整的 Markdown 格式文章内容（不要包含 H1 标题）\",\n  \"tags\": [\"标签1\", \"标签2\", \"标签3\"]\n}\n\n要求：\n- 使用适当的标题（H2 为章节标题，H3 为小节标题）\n- 包含引言和结论\n- 使用专业且引人入胜的语调\n- 目标 800-1500 字\n- 使用 Markdown 格式\n- 建议 3-5 个相关标签\n- 仅返回 JSON 对象，不要返回其他内容"

msgid "Write a complete, well-structured article with the title: \"%1$s\"%2$s%3$s\n\nRequirements:\n- Start with the title as a markdown H1 heading\n- Use proper headings (H2 for sections, H3 for subsections)\n- Include an introduction and conclusion\n- Write in a professional yet engaging tone\n- Aim for 800-1500 words\n- Use markdown formatting"
msgstr "撰写一篇标题为 \"%1$s\" 的完整、结构清晰的文章。%2$s%3$s\n\n要求：\n- 以 Markdown H1 标题开头\n- 使用适当的标题（H2 为章节标题，H3 为小节标题）\n- 包含引言和结论\n- 使用专业且引人入胜的语调\n- 目标 800-1500 字\n- 使用 Markdown 格式"

msgid "You are a professional content writer for a WordPress blog. Write clear, engaging, and SEO-friendly content. Always respond in the same language as the user's request. You must respond with valid JSON only."
msgstr "你是一位专业的 WordPress 博客内容撰稿人。请撰写清晰、引人入胜且 SEO 友好的内容。始终使用与用户请求相同的语言回复。必须仅返回有效的 JSON。"

msgid "You are a professional content writer for a WordPress blog. Write clear, engaging, and SEO-friendly content. Always respond in the same language as the user's request. Output markdown directly."
msgstr "你是一位专业的 WordPress 博客内容撰稿人。请撰写清晰、引人入胜且 SEO 友好的内容。始终使用与用户请求相同的语言回复。直接输出 Markdown。"

